Package: myRepository
Title: Utilities aiding package development and maintenance of your own internal R package repository
Version: 1.34.0
Date: 2019-09-17
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Tilford", email = "charles.tilford@bms.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Includes functions to create an internal repository, add
    .tar.gz pacakges to it and build supporting files like the
    manifest. Also generates a "pretty" table summarizing the packages
    that will be displayed when visiting the repository root
    URL. Additional tools generate empty package structures with
    example toy code to illustrate the use and misuse of Roxygen,
    guidance on filling out DESCRIPTION, and testing examples. A
    build-and-check method wraps up building and checking of the code.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports:
    devtools (>= 1.11.0),
    utils,
    callr,
    crayon,
    desc,
    dynamictable,
    openssl,
    CatMisc (>= 0.8.5),
    testthat,
    roxygen2,
    htmltools
URL: https://biogit.pri.bms.com/tilfordc/myRepository
BugReports: https://biogit.pri.bms.com/tilfordc/myRepository/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
